title: Annual report
context: [ยง334B-8] Annual report. The director shall submit an annual report to the governor and the legislature at least twenty days prior to the convening of each regular session concerning the conduct of review agents that have been reported to the complaint resolution panel. The report shall include an analysis of complaints filed against agents by patients or their representatives, or providers. [L 1991, c 95, pt of ยง1]
